outcomes: I got puke on my favourite t-shirt :(
I ended with a precious ring in my pocket and accidentally sold it on a black-marketplace... oops!
A very cute person stayed all night by my side and we went to talk to a more intimate place about life and the stars... Life sometimes is like a movie!

activities.activityName: Go on a date with someone from a dating app
outcomes: It was weird... They didn't ask a single question! I wasted my time...
They didn't look like their profile AT ALL, so I ran away before they saw me!
They were as nervous as me, and somehow that made it lovelier! I'm going to ask them on a second date!!

activities.activityName: Go to a café alone and act mysterious
outcomes: I spilled the coffee all over my dress! I felt pathetic!
I sat in the café thinking all love ever does is break and burn, and end...
I was about to slip with my coffee but a very handsome person caught me in the air and they made me company!
I stayed by the door all night long and they never came... I hate it here!
I tried inviting my crush, but they couldn't come... But my friends came to cheer me up!
None of my friends could come so I went to the nearest Chinese food store and found my crush and I invited them to come! It was great!!

activities.activityName: Prepare a fancy dinner and lay by the phone
outcomes: It was a disaster! The food tasted horrible and nobody texted me! I feel like dark tumblr 2014 posts...
I'm starting to believe my phone is broken, because I didn't receive any messages! At least the food was really good I guess...
I almost burnt the kitchen down! But I was fast and called the firefighters and a handsome and strong one came to help extinguish it and asked me on a date!!
Every popular person in high school was there, and let me tell you they aged like rotten milk! I couldn't stand it so I left early
I have never seen a disco more old-fashioned and boring! Luckily someone bought a bottle of champagne and forgot about it!
I crashed into my high school sweetheart and they confessed they had a crush on me back then!! They are still the most beautiful person I have ever seen!
I couldn't believe it when I saw them showing up in THAT outfit... It seems that it was really a BLIND date...
It was not a match I fear... But at least the food and the place was really good!
I think I fell in love the moment I saw them showing up with a Gilmore Girls t-shirt, listening to Taylor Swift and saying they love The Smiths!

activities.activityName: Read a pretentious book in the park
outcomes: Now I understand why it's called pretentious... It was awful! Never reading anything by a man ever again
Did you know the father's DNA stays inside the mother for seven years? Now I don't think I want to have children...
A cute person sat next to me on the bench and we both read peacefully till the sun set up... When I was about to leave, they said they waited all afternoon to ask for my number!
Everyone there was old! VERY OLD! And they kept stepping on my feet!!
I thought they were going to be romantic, but they ended up being a bunch of moms dancing together and gossiping... I LOVE IT!
I was out of breath when my assigned partner looked sculpted by the angels! I assure you that the rest of the afternoon was pure FUEGO
